title: China Camp’s enduring beauty beckons
text:
Photo: Eric Risberg, Associated Press China Camp State Park is a former 19th Century Chinese shrimping village on the northern shores of San Francisco Bay. China Camp State Park is a former 19th Century Chinese shrimping...
You don’t need to be a multimillionaire to own one of the finest shoreline properties in the Bay Area. All you need is $5 to park your car. That gets you ownership for your visit.
